name: Headings Are Important
description: Search engines use the headings to index the structure and content of your web pages. Users often skim a page by its headings. It is important to use headings to show the document structure.

name: Bigger Headings
description: Each HTML heading has a default size. However, you can specify the size for any heading with the style attribute, using the CSS font-size property
